    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <pb n="1" xml:id="p.1"/>
                <opener>
                    <stamp sameAs="stamp.83">
                        <orgName key="org.194">Verlag Helianthus</orgName>, Berlin <lb/>
                        <placeName key="place.2.4.1">Berlin-Halensee</placeName>.</stamp>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Herrn <persName key="pers.3263">Arnold Schönberg</persName>
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Komponist.</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Wien IX</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            <placeName key="place.9.11.1.2">Liechtensteinstr. 68/70.</placeName>
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                </opener>
                <pb n="2" xml:id="p.2"/>
                <opener>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Herrn <persName key="pers.3263">Arnold Schönberg</persName>,
                                <placeName key="place.9.11">Wien</placeName>.
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                </opener>
                <salute>Sehr geehrter Herr.</salute>
                <p>Wir fragen höfl. an, wann wir <lb/>die Korrekturen der am <date when="1907-10-16">16. Oktober 07</date>
                    <lb/>geschickten Stimmen zu Ihrem <bibl sameAs="werke.42">op 7</bibl>
                    <lb/>zurück erwarten können.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute rendition="#r">Hochachtungsvoll</salute>
                    <lb/>
                    <stamp sameAs="stamp.50" rendition="#r">
                        <orgName key="org.180">VERLAG
                            DREILILIEN</orgName>.</stamp>
                    <lb/>
                    <stamp sameAs="stamp.109">
                        <placeName key="place.2.4.1">Berlin-Halensee</placeName>, den <date when="1907-11-27">
                            <seg hand="#author">27. November</seg> 190<seg hand="#author">7</seg>
                        </date>
                    </stamp>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
